These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, salsa, techno, d&b
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of house##1
2. the person eating mango is the fan of d&b##1
3. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of house##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
5. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | house     | techno   | d&b |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, september, december, march
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, soccer, swimming, volleyball
1. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | december | march | september | november    |
| Sport   | swimming    | soccer      | parkour | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, rock-climbing, traveling, writing
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, bus, helicopter, tram
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | fishing | writing | traveling   | rock-climbing |
| Transport   | train   | helicopter | tram | bus         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, drama, western
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, milk, lemonade, 7up
1. the person drinking milk is the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the person drinking water is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | western | disaster | action  | drama      |
| Beverage         | milk | 7up   | lemonade | water |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, fishing, filmmaking, cooking
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, hedgehog, pony
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Hobby   | cooking | filmmaking | fishing | dancing |
| Pet    | dog       | pony | hedgehog | hamster     |

