.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, mexican, nigerian, pakistani
There 4 different types of food: spinach, cucumber, kiwi, broccoli
1. the mexican is on the far right##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
4. the person eating spinach is on the left of the nigerian##1
5. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | nigerian | dutch | mexican |
| Food           | spinach      | kiwi | broccoli | cucumber    |

