.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, indie, salsa
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, february, december, november
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
3. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | indie | electronic | classical | salsa  |
| Birthday           | december | may | november       | february |

