.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, chaman, davidoff, aristoff
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, tram, trike
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
2. the person driving the trike is the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
4. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the car is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Cigar         | davidoff | montecristo      | chaman | aristoff |
| Transport   | car          | quad-bike | tram     | trike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, spy, zombie
4 different pets are kept: fish, mouse, dog, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | spy       | family | zombie   |
| Pet     | mouse | dog | hedgehog   | fish |

