The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, cycling, basketball, climbing
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | cola | milk  | hot-chocolate | sprite |
| Sport   | climbing | basketball | cycling          | swimming    |

