.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, tram, snowmobile, ship
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, d&b, disco, r&b
1. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of blues##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of disco##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the tram is the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Transport      | snowmobile | tram  | train | ship |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | disco | r&b           | d&b   |

