.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-13::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, social-worker, teacher, scientist
4 different pets are kept: hamster, lizard, rabbit, rat
1. the owner of the rat is the lawyer##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the lawyer##1
3. the teacher is the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the teacher is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
5. the scientist is on the right of the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Job   | teacher | social-worker  | lawyer | scientist   |
| Pet        | rabbit | lizard | rat    | hamster |

