.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-15::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, green, blood-red, purple
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, skateboarding, soccer, swimming
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |    4     |
| Color   | blood-red | purple     | grey | green |
| Sport         | swimming | skateboarding | parkour   | soccer   |

