2. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
5. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Sport         | skateboarding | handball | parkour | cycling |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | scientific    | action      | drama   |

