.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, snake, pony, mouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, car, scooter, snowmobile
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
4. the owner of the mouse is the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the boat is on the left of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Pet   | dog | pony | snake | mouse   |
| Transport     | scooter  | boat    | car       | snowmobile |

 